                            <comment id="129409" author="gerrit" created="Tue, 6 Oct 2015 01:57:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oleg Drokin (oleg.drokin@intel.com) merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/16667/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/16667/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
